SkillPilot AI
About
SkillPilot AI is an AI-powered Learning & Growth Platform designed for software engineering teams. It replaces static Excel-based growth plans with personalized learning paths, AI-generated content, daily micro‑missions, and progress dashboards.

Hackathon Goals
During the hackathon, teams will build a working MVP that demonstrates:

Personalized learning :

Generates personalized learning journeys for engineers

AI‑generated learning content :

Uses AI to create content, quizzes, missions, and summaries
Track learner progress over time
Gamified micro‑learning : Makes learning engaging through gamification

Dashboards for learners and managers to gives visibility into team growth
Your MVP should show how AI can transform the learning experience inside a software development company.\

Teams may innovate further, creativity is encouraged.

Details Personas :

- Learner (Software Engineer)

Wants guidance, structure, and motivation
Has limited time due to meetings and sprint work
Needs personalized learning instead of generic content

Manager / OD Team / Admin :

- Oversees employee growth
  Needs progress visibility & skill insights
  Must identify drop‑offs and bottlenecks
